ood with a hippie mother only caring for her affairs, Michael, a molecular biologist, is more interested in genes than women, while Bruno is obsessed with his sexual desires, but mostly finds his satisfaction with prostitutes.  But Bruno's life changes when he gets to know the experienced Christiane.  In the meantime, Michael meets Annabelle, the love of his youth, again.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.4854,"vote_count":146,"poster_path":"/wpGpR7GewyApPgqPvuWadBAfmFc.jpg","release_date":"2006-02-10","vote_average":6.12,"backdrop_path":"/60PJPzXtQmLQdaCNuWUrrHe1mzu.jpg","original_title":"Elementarteilchen","original_language":"de"},{"id":99,"adult":false,"title":"All About My Mother","video":false,"overview":"Following the tragic death of her teenage son, Manuela travels from Madrid to Barcelona in an attempt to contact the long-estranged father the boy never knew. She reunites with an old friend, an outspoken transgender sex worker, and befriends a troubled actress and a pregnant, HIV-positive nun.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":2.4504,"vote_count":2027,"poster_path":"/hjQhzhkGYXPNM96k0mOgob6HMmn.jpg","release_date":"1999-04-16","vote_average":7.628,"backdrop_path":"/tilClWjFZeUTGJu0pxgF72fvUmN.jpg","original_title":"Todo sobre mi madre","original_language":"es"},{"id":271218,"adult":false,"title":"The Sob","video":false,"overview":"After his mother had died, Kenan (Muzaffer Tema) left the home to take care of a goodhearted rich man, whose daughter Nalan (Nedret Güvenç) fell deeply in love with him...","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.1475,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/8aHiTlq4CXZ0JcaOxRwTYiBYtLn.jpg","release_date":"1953-01-01","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Hıçkırık","original_language":"tr"},{"id":143,"adult":false,"title":"All Quiet on the Western Front","video":false,"overview":"When a group of idealistic young men join the German Army during the Great War, they are assigned to the Western Front, where their patriotism 